data.description: This tudor style Colonial nestled in the heart of Sherwood Forest offers spacious living at its best! Gleaming hardwoods accessorize this 5 bedroom, 3 full and 1 half bath home. Stone fireplace, updated kitchen and fully finished lower level complete this Colonial style home. Enormous backyard and deck provide privacy and space for outdoor living. Close proximity to Subase, Casinos and Electric Boat. Pet flexible, non-smoking,credit check and 1 year (minimum) Lease Agreement are required.
